sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_15eb8e5fdb5473406529f7e33996190c
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.URLwandering</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description>Usage: 

var url_wandering = new URLwandering;
url_wandering.execute();</description><name>URLwandering</name><script><![CDATA[var URLwandering = Class.create();
URLwandering.prototype = {
	initialize: function(minutesAgo) {
		if(!minutesAgo) minutesAgo = gs.getProperty("url.wander.poll_interval");
		this.timeMinutesAgo = this.getTimeMinutesAgo(minutesAgo);
	},
	
	_getUserById: function(username) {
		
		var gr = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
		gr.addQuery("user_name",username);
		gr.query();
		
		if(gr.next()) {
			return gr.sys_id;
		} else {
			return false;
		}
	},
	
	hasNoRole: function(username) {
		var gr = new GlideRecord("sys_user_has_role");
		gr.addQuery("user",this._getUserById(username));
		gr.addQuery("role","!=","7fcaa702933002009c8579b4f47ffbde");  // exclude users with snc_internal role
		gr.query();
		
		if(gr.hasNext()) {
			return false;
		} else {
			return true;
		}
	},
	
	getTimeMinutesAgo: function(m) {
		
		var ms = 1000 * 60 * m;
		var now = new GlideDateTime();
		now.subtract(ms);
		return now.getValue();
	},
	
	getUsersInTimeframe: function() {
		var users = [];
		
		var gr = new GlideAggregate("syslog_transaction");
		gr.addQuery("sys_created_on",">=",this.timeMinutesAgo);
		gr.addAggregate("count","sys_created_by");
		gr.groupBy("sys_created_by");
		gr.query();
		
		while(gr.next()) {
			if(this.hasNoRole(gr.sys_created_by)) {
				users.push(gr.sys_created_by.toString());
			}
		}
		
		return users;
	},
	
	hasWandered: function(user_name) {
		var tr = new GlideRecord("syslog_transaction");
		tr.addQuery("sys_created_on",">=",this.timeMinutesAgo);
		tr.addQuery("type","IN","list,form");
		tr.addQuery("url","DOES NOT CONTAIN","/sp/");
		tr.addQuery("sys_created_by",user_name);
		
		var whitelist = gs.getProperty("url.wander.whitelist").split(",");
		for(i=0; i<whitelist.length; i++) {
			tr.addQuery("url","DOES NOT CONTAIN",whitelist[i]);
		}
		
		tr.query();
		gs.print(user_name + ":" + tr.getRowCount());
		
		while(tr.next()) {
			gs.eventQueue("url.wander",tr,user_name,tr.url);
		} 
	},
	
	execute: function() {
		var users = this.getUsersInTimeframe();
		var w;	
		for(i=0; i<users.length-1; i++) {
			w = this.hasWandered(users[i]);
		}
	},
	
	type: 'URLwandering'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-25 13:37:21</sys_created_on><sys_id>15eb8e5fdb5473406529f7e33996190c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>84</sys_mod_count><sys_name>URLwandering</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_15eb8e5fdb5473406529f7e33996190c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-26 14:05:43</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
